As a user(customer) 
I want to be able to make my purchase via different payment methods (ApplePay, GooglePay).
So that I can choose which one fits me the best


Scope

Add different types of payment system
Checkout functionality
Customers should be able to select the different types of payment
It should work in Chrome, Mozilla, Safari browsers
It should also work in Mobile


Precondition:

The item is added to the card
The checkout page is opened

Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1:User can successfully select the payment method and to continue confirm buying the item
Given: User on the "Checkout" page
When: Select the payment type
Then: The appropriate payment method (ApplePay, GooglePay) is selected and the user is able to continue to confirm purchase product



Scenario 2 The user can not successfully continue to confirm purchase product without selecting the payment method
Given: User on the "Checkout" page
When: Click on the "Continue" button without selecting the payment method
Then: The error message is shown on the page







